<header>
<div class='post-title'>
<h2>
<a href="simple-audit-gem-updates-for-rails3">&#x27;Simple Audit&#x27; gem patch for Rails3</a>
</h2>
</div>
</header>
<div class='post-body' id='post_body_123334'>
<p>In Rails3 all strings are escaped by default, in <a href="https://github.com/gtarnovan/simple_audit">Simple Audit</a> this doubly escapes the html output of the audit history display. While waiting for the main trunk to be updated I forked the main repo and created a version that explicitly outputs the audit history in raw format so that it can be displayed.</p>
<p>If you want to try it you can get my fork of simple audit:Â <a href="https://github.com/vfilby/simple_audit">https://github.com/vfilby/simple_audit</a></p>
</div>

